text: Unzaga is a surname of Basque origins that may refer to *Luis de Unzaga (1721–1790), Spanish Governor of Louisiana *Jon Unzaga (born 1962), Spanish cyclist *Óscar Únzaga (1916–1959), Bolivian political figure and rebel *Ramón Unzaga (1894–1923), Spanish-Chilean football player Category:Basque-language surnames
title: Unzaga
